OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773745530
OL,3,CFamily of woman shot by her own father
OL,4,Cfelt 'abandoned' by Foreign Office
OL,6,FThe mother of a woman who was shot in
OL,7,Fthe chest by her own father has said
OL,8,Fshe felt "totally abandoned" by the
OL,9,FForeign Office.
OL,11,FLucy Harrison, 23, had been staying
OL,12,Fwith her father Kris Harrison and his
OL,13,Ffamily in Prosper, Texas, in January
OL,14,F2025 when she was killed after being
OL,15,Fshot in the chest.
OL,17,FMr Harrison said in a statement that
OL,18,Fhe "lifted the gun to show her" when
OL,19,Fhe heard a loud bang.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
