OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773745530
OL,3,CFamily of woman shot by her own father
OL,4,Cfelt 'abandoned' by Foreign Office
OL,6,FHe said: "I did not understand what
OL,7,Fhad happened. Lucy immediately fell."
OL,9,FLucy's mum, Jane Coates, said she
OL,10,Freceived an email from the Foreign
OL,11,FOffice two days after Lucy's death
OL,12,Fwith an attachment of a "guide for
OL,13,Fbereaved families", but was offered no
OL,14,Ffurther support.
OL,16,FShe said: "In a state of shock and
OL,17,Fconfusion - my daughter had just been
OL,18,Fshot and killed abroad - I wanted a
OL,19,Freal person who would be my advocate."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773745530
OL,3,CFamily of woman shot by her own father
OL,4,Cfelt 'abandoned' by Foreign Office
OL,6,FA grand jury in the US determined
OL,7,Fthere was insufficient evidence to
OL,8,Fcharge anyone in connection with Ms
OL,9,FHarrison's death, but a UK inquest
OL,10,Fruled she was "killed unlawfully".
OL,12,FThe fashion buyer from Warrington,
OL,13,FCheshire, had travelled to America
OL,14,Fwith her boyfriend, Sam Littler, for a
OL,15,Fholiday after her dad moved when she
OL,16,Fwas a child, Cheshire Coroner's Court
OL,17,Fwas told.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773745530
OL,3,CFamily of woman shot by her own father
OL,4,Cfelt 'abandoned' by Foreign Office
OL,6,FGiving evidence at the UK inquest, Mr
OL,7,FLittler said Ms Harrison would often
OL,8,Fbecome upset with her dad, who the
OL,9,Finquest heard had previously been to
OL,10,Frehab for alcohol addiction, when he
OL,11,Fspoke about his ownership of a gun.
OL,13,FMr Harrison said he had bought the gun
OL,14,Fa couple of years before because he
OL,15,Fwanted a "sense of security" for his
OL,16,Ffamily and denied ever discussing it
OL,17,Fwith his daughter before.
OL,19,FHe said a licence is not required when
OL,20,Fa gun is owned for home defence in
OL,21,FTexas.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773745530
OL,3,CFamily of woman shot by her own father
OL,4,Cfelt 'abandoned' by Foreign Office
OL,6,FJane said: "Everybody that knew Lucy
OL,7,Fwould know that she wouldn't want to
OL,8,Fsee the gun. The coroner described
OL,9,FKris as a teaser in his character, and
OL,10,Fyet I just can't understand why he
OL,11,Ffelt the need to show Lucy that gun."
OL,13,FMs Harrison's family are calling for
OL,14,Fpolice in the US to re-open the case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773745530
OL,3,CFamily of woman shot by her own father
OL,4,Cfelt 'abandoned' by Foreign Office
OL,6,FMs Coates said the funeral director
OL,7,Fcontacted the coroner when she saw Ms
OL,8,FHarrison's body, as she had "concerns
OL,9,Fwith the information she had received"
OL,10,Fthat it was an accident and that Ms
OL,11,FHarrison had been standing next to her
OL,12,Ffather during the incident.
OL,14,FJane said: "I don't believe that
OL,15,F(Kris) meant to intentionally kill his
OL,16,Fdaughter. The coroner said she
OL,17,Faccepted he wasn't aware that there
OL,18,Fwas a loaded bullet in the chamber but
OL,19,Fmy point is he should have been aware."
OL,26,@wD@ApmwD@Fpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
