OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773745530
OL,3,CFamily of woman shot by her own father
OL,4,Cfelt 'abandoned' by Foreign Office
OL,6,FA Foreign Office spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Our thoughts remain with Jane and her
OL,8,Ffamily for the tragic loss they have
OL,9,Fsuffered, and we will always look to
OL,10,Flearn lessons from cases such as this
OL,11,Fone to improve the consular support we
OL,12,Foffer to other families in the future."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
